  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit",
    "In a blender, combine lime juice, olive oil, ají amarillo pepper, garlic, salt, and black pepper to make the mantecare emulsify",
    "In a large bowl, mix together the mashed yellow potato, chopped cilantro, and sliced ume plum",
    "Add the mantecare emulsify to the potato mixture and stir until well combined",
    "Spoon the mixture into a baking dish and smooth the top",
    "Bake for 20 minutes or until the top is lightly browned",
    "Remove from the oven and let cool for a few minutes",
    "Serve warm and enjoy"
